{"tid":2414521,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇邊個歌手可以勤力得過00-08既周杰倫？","createTime":"2021-02-19T12:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T06:19:53.000Z","uid":1627,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe334647ae8bf972d58f6e50767f76c3fe8fe80","tid":2414521,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"一年出一隻碟，全部自己作曲同操刀，頭幾隻仲要公認係神碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要每首歌都拍mv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係佢碟裡面既每一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要拍埋電影，不能說的秘密同頭文字D我諗都算係經典作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要開左幾次巡迴演唱會，無與倫比同07又係華語演唱會經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要瘋狂作歌比其他歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加加埋埋都夠出幾隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗諗下可能有啲歌手一世都冇佢呢幾年咁勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94463c2a5081c513442b5de584a3dadc5fd0437","tid":2414521,"uid":1627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"有啲歌手隔幾年每次揀返幾首以前作品+返一兩首新歌就當新碟出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再對比返周杰倫一年10幾首新歌你就明點解佢啲代表作品會特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f438918524795af916c500f8c1d45b6e803fa8a","tid":2414521,"uid":10903,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:49:48.000Z","msg":"當劉華冇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港公認最勤力"},{"pid":"a6e4b692ce28656e84c31055f1d8bec49c2cb52e","tid":2414521,"uid":47658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:51:18.000